column2: SELECT s.specObjID, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, s.zErr, s.class, s.zWarning, s.snMedian, g.ra, g.dec, zp.z, zp.zErr into mydb.result_zoo2 from mydb.zoo2Main as g CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjEq (g.ra, g.dec, #) AS near JOIN SpecObjAll as s ON near.specObjID = s.specObjID JOIN Photoz as zp ON zp.objID = s.bestObjID
